 Two family members close to the couple told Sunday World that Khumalo met Tshwanelo Ntshudisane at a funeral in Kgabalatsane village, north of Pretoria."Doctor eyed Tshwanelo during the funeral but he was scared to talk to her there. He asked for her numbers from her family members after everyone had dispersed from the funeral."The two started chatting through WhatsApp two days after the funeral and started seeing each other," said the family member.TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE 